    <item>
      <title>Validation.apply</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-apply/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-apply/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.apply&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;validation&amp;#32;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Applies a validation-wrapped function to a validation-wrapped value.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;(&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value -&amp;gt; &amp;rsquo;next&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The validation containing the function.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;value&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The validation containing the value.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The result of applying the function to the value, with accumulated errors.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.at</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-at/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-at/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.at&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;path&amp;#32;validation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Scopes a validation under the supplied path segments.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;path&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-pathsegment.html&#34;&gt;PathSegment&lt;/a&gt; list&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The path segments to apply to the validation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The validation to scope.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A validation nested under the given path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.bind</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-bind/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-bind/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.bind&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;binder&amp;#32;validation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Sequences a validation-producing continuation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;remarks&#34;&gt;Remarks&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is the monadic &amp;ldquo;bind&amp;rdquo; for validation. Note that this operation short-circuits&#xA;and does not accumulate errors from the binder if the source has already failed.&#xA;For accumulation, use &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/map2&#34;&gt;map2&lt;/a&gt; or the applicative &lt;code&gt;and!&lt;/code&gt; syntax.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;binder&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value -&amp;gt; &lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;next, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;A function of type &lt;code&gt;&#39;value -&amp;gt; Validation&amp;lt;&#39;next, &#39;error&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The source validation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The result of the binder or the original diagnostics.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.collect</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-collect/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-collect/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.collect&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;validations&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Collects a sequence of validations into a single validation of a list.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;remarks&#34;&gt;Remarks&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This operation is applicative: it will collect errors from ALL items in the sequence.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validations&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; seq&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;A sequence of type &lt;code&gt;seq&amp;lt;Validation&amp;lt;&#39;value, &#39;error&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A validation containing the list of values or accumulated diagnostics.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.error</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-error/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-error/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.error&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;diagnostics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Creates a failing validation result with the provided diagnostics.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;diagnostics&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-diagnostics-1.html&#34;&gt;Diagnostics&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;rsquo;error&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-diagnostics-1.html&#34;&gt;Diagnostics&lt;/a&gt; graph.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A failing &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.fail</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-fail/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-fail/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.fail&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;diagnostics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Alias for &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/error&#34;&gt;error&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;diagnostics&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-diagnostics-1.html&#34;&gt;Diagnostics&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;rsquo;error&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-diagnostics-1.html&#34;&gt;Diagnostics&lt;/a&gt; graph.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A failing &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.fromResult</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-fromresult/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-fromresult/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.fromResult&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;result&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Lifts a standard &lt;a href=&#34;https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.result-2&#34;&gt;Result&lt;/a&gt; into the &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt; context.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;remarks&#34;&gt;Remarks&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If the result is an error, it is wrapped in a root-level &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-diagnostics-1.html&#34;&gt;Diagnostics&lt;/a&gt; graph.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;result&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://fsharp.github.io/fsharp-core-docs/reference/fsharp-core-fsharpresult-2&#34;&gt;Result&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The result to lift.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt; mirroring the result.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.ignore</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-ignore/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-ignore/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.ignore&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;validation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Maps a successful validation value to &lt;code&gt;unit&lt;/code&gt; while preserving the diagnostics.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The source validation.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A validation that keeps the original diagnostics and discards the success value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.index</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-index/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.index&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;index&amp;#32;validation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Prefixes a validation with an indexed branch.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;index&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;int&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The branch index.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The validation to scope.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A validation whose diagnostics are prefixed with &lt;code&gt;Index index&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Validation.key</title>
      <link>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-key/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:3000/reference/validation/m-validation-key/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;fsdocs-usage&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;Validation.key&amp;#32;&lt;span&gt;key&amp;#32;validation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Prefixes a validation with a keyed branch.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;parameters&#34;&gt;Parameters&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;key&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;string&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The branch key.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;validation&lt;/code&gt;: &lt;code&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://adz.github.io/FsFlow/reference/FsFlow/fsflow-validation-2.html&#34;&gt;Validation&lt;/a&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;lsquo;value, &amp;rsquo;error&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&#xA;The validation to scope.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;returns&#34;&gt;Returns&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A validation whose diagnostics are prefixed with &lt;code&gt;Key key&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
